    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">Can you eat Costco hot dogs on keto? Macro breakdown, low-carb serving suggestions, and modifications for ketogenic diet.</p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-10 mb-4">Macro Breakdown for Keto Diet</h2>
